'''''Great Tomb, Hide the Secrets of Incarnations''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[Back to Earth in Evernight]].

==Steps==
# Continue forward deeper into the Great Tomb
# Collect Titan Runes in This Area
# Continue forward deeper into the Great Tomb
# Encapsulate the Encryption Key and Download Runes
# Continue forward and head to the Central Access Platform
# Upload the encryption key
# Continue forward and head to the new sector
# Continue forward deeper into the Great Tomb
# Collect Death Titan Runes
# Continue forward and head to the next area
# Collect Trickster Titan Runes
# Collect Strife Titan Runes
# Encapsulate the Encryption Key and Download Runes
# Head to the Central Access Platform and upload the encryption key
# Continue forward and head to the new sector
# Continue forward deeper into the Great Tomb
